infos.info: Dunning lists Joseph Kearns as Sgt. Matt Grebb in 1950, then Wally Maher (not Mayer)from ca.1951. Also as cast members: Raymond Burr, Jeanette Nolan, Sheldon Leonard. Music by Eddie Dunstedter. Producer-Director in 1950 Elliot Lewis. Writers listed as: Morton Fine, David Friedkin, Blake Edwards.
